Package model.gameMaze.solver

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Distance
    Distance interface - distance from node to node
    Domain
    Domain interface
    Searcher
    Searcher interface that represents algorithms of search
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbsSearcher
    Abstract class that is type of searcher, this class represents all searchers that uses openList and closedList.
    Maze
    Maze class - holds a data member of type int[][] that represents a 2D matrix that is our maze.
    MazeAction
    Holds x,y and adds them to the Node's point .
    MazeAirDistance
    Heuristic of distance - square root of rows^2 + columns^2, rows from goal and columns from goal.
    MazeDistanceG
    Straight moves cost 10 and diagonal cost 15.
    MazeDomain
    Maze Domain class.
    Node
    Node class - holds a data member of type Point that represents the node, and g and f that are used in search algorithms .
    NodeMazeActionPair
    Class that holds a node with an action
